{
  "stem": "6736.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I stayed by myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I asked the guy who was in charge, the judenrein, the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And if he will take me home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he had mercy on me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He took me home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I stayed there for a few days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He had a little store, a grocery.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I opened the store.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I wrote home that I'm going to leave Biala Podlaska and I'm coming home, back to Krakow.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I got a return letter from my uncle-- from my father and mother not to come because they already received papers that they will also be shipped in the area of Biala Podlaska.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Sure enough, it was between Purim-- I was Purim in Biala Podlaska-- between Purim and Pesach, was in middle of March or beginning of April, my entire family was shipped to Miedzyrzec.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Miedzyrzec, [NON-ENGLISH] was 21 kilometer-- that was a 14, 15 miles-- from Biala Podlaska.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One morning, I'm walking in the street in Biala Podlaska, I see my father.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, Dad, what are you-- what are you doing here?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, we all live on the-- I came to get you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we're going-- I rented a home in Miedzyrzec.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we're going to be all together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went to Miedzyrzec.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in April, and May, and June, my older brother and myself went halfway from Miedzyrzec to Biala Podlaska to work in the forests.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We worked for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We got paid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We worked for the Germans to cut the, the forest and to prepare it for an airport.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And first we laid an airport.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And at the end of the airport, you cut out the trees where a plane can go in and hide there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The forests there were very thick.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
